WEBVTT

00:00.030 --> 00:01.355
<i>Previously on Switched at Birth...</i>

00:01.398 --> 00:03.147
<i>People are calling you la malinche.</i>

00:03.183 --> 00:04.248
Cortes' whore?

00:04.284 --> 00:07.085
What happens when your
landlords double our rent?

00:07.120 --> 00:09.103
I pulled out of East Riverside.

00:09.155 --> 00:10.521
- I'm Iris.
- Daphne.

00:10.523 --> 00:12.323
I'm in the interpreter program.

00:12.359 --> 00:13.441
Do you know a guy named Robbie?

00:13.493 --> 00:15.126
Yes, I know who you're talking about.

00:15.161 --> 00:16.361
Is there somewhere I
can leave this for him?

00:16.413 --> 00:17.528
Why don't I just give it to him?

00:17.530 --> 00:19.330
Didn't I make it clear that I'm with him?

00:19.366 --> 00:20.748
Stay away from him.

00:20.784 --> 00:23.334
You didn't know that the turkey
sandwich that you so stupidly handed over

00:23.370 --> 00:26.170
to an inmate had a bag of
heroin stuffed inside it?

00:26.206 --> 00:27.205
Oh my God.

00:27.207 --> 00:30.174
You just became an accessory
to a felony drug deal.

00:30.210 --> 00:33.344
Professor Marillo, I heard that
your "Chemistry 1" class was filled,

00:33.380 --> 00:36.097
and I was hoping to
persuade you to let me in.

00:36.132 --> 00:37.215
You have an interpreter?

00:37.217 --> 00:39.217
We go 90 miles an hour.

00:39.269 --> 00:41.386
Get someone who knows what
the hell they're talking about,

00:41.438 --> 00:43.104
or you will drown.

00:43.139 --> 00:45.390
Josh, this is my roommate Daphne.

00:45.392 --> 00:47.225
I have a proposition for you.

00:47.227 --> 00:49.527
We will text constantly.

00:49.528 --> 00:53.151
_

00:53.203 --> 00:54.282
It's the right decision.

