01:17.390 --> 01:19.524
<i>♪ Whether you have lost your way ♪</i>

01:21.261 --> 01:23.394
<i>♪ whether you have doubted me ♪</i>

01:24.514 --> 01:27.866
<i>- ♪ whether you are dirty or clean ♪
